  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546310/extras/fae14feb4fa533b0c555acbe44d78b98.avif?t=1773942954\" width=560 height=130 /></span><br>Blocks turn into sand - clear pixels by connecting the same color across the screen.<br><br>Sandtrix+ is an expanded version of the freeware game Sandtrix.<br>It extends the base game with new game modes, challenging color modes, and unlockable themes and effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546310/extras/26f2d101629053b84237a2221d3c4dde.avif?t=1773942954\" width=448 height=194 /></span><br><br>This game is DRM-Free, fully portable and does not connect to the internet.<br>If you like this game please consider supporting the developer and buying the full version.<br><br><u>Streamers: Streaming this game and monetizing said streams is allowed and does not need further permission.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546310/extras/efdac61fbf3df9315183d4271b9850cc.poster.avif?t=1773942954\" width=316 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546310/extras/efdac61fbf3df9315183d4271b9850cc.webm?t=1773942954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2546310/extras/efdac61fbf3df9315183d4271b9850cc.mp4?t=1773942954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
